  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Update the safety plan with details of the hardware development phase. Specifically regarding activities to determine&#xD;
    the correct methods and measures that are&amp;nbsp; to be used to ensure functional safety of the hardware elements of the&#xD;
    design.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The safety plan is based upon the activities for the HW product development described in ISO 26262, Volume 5, clauses&#xD;
    6-10, and it references the reference phase model for the HW development phase, as detailed in ISO 26262, clause 5.2.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To refine the safety plan to take into account HW development.</purpose>
